replies.msg:
做frontend 通常都要跟designer 嘅設計，做電話同電腦兩個版本。通常睇designer 設計嘅program 都只會show 一個用px 做單位嘅size 畀你跟，如果想偷懶，唔寫media query, 可以用我新寫嘅plugin, Bewater, 自動將px 邊做clamp(), 全自動解決responsive 嘅問題<br />
<br />
<a href="https://github.com/winston0410/bewater" data-sr-url="https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fwinston0410%2Fbewater&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIubV8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=0b473f45" data-auto-link target="_blank">https://github.com/winston0410/bewater</a><br />
<br />
示範：<br />
<br />
<pre><code data-type="css">
/* Before transformation */
p {
  font-size: 30px;
  padding: 15px;
}</code></pre><br />
<br />
<pre><code data-type="javascript">//postcss.config.js
module.exports = {
  plugins: [
    //Other plugins...

    require('postcss-sparrow')({
      transformations: [
        {
          selectors: ['*'],
          inclusion: true,
          callbacks: [
            require('bewater')(
              {
                props: {
                  props: ['font-size'],
                  inclusion: true
                },
                units: {
                  units: ['*'],
                  inclusion: true
                },
                scale: 1.5, //Multiplier for the original value, and the product will be used as the 3rd param for clamp()
                changeRate: '4vw' //The rate for the value to change.  This value will be used as the 2nd param for clamp()
              }
            )
          ]
        }
      ]
    })
  ]
}</code></pre><br />
<br />
<pre><code data-type="css">/* After transformation */
p {
  font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 45px);
  padding: 15px;
}</code></pre>
